name: Blokshot VR
summary: Take your gaming skills to the next level with Blokshot VR! This fast-paced, action-packed shooter combines classic arcade gameplay with futuristic immersive VR gameplay, for an unbeatable experience. Compete against other Oculus players, Rack up high scores and climb to the top of the leaderboard as you blast your way through a geometric cascade of fast paced shooter action.  Put your reflexes to the test, using a range of unique weaponry to maximize your combos. The excitement doesn't stop there -...
